    "category": "section",
    "text": "(gdb) break jl_apply_generic if strcmp((char*)(jl_symbol_name)(jl_gf_mtable(F)->name), \"method_to_break\")==0Since this function is used for every call, you will make everything 1000x slower if you do this."
